<!DOCTYPE article PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD Simplified DocBook XML V1.2CR1//EN" "http://www.docbook.org/xml/simple/1.2CR1/sdocbook.dtd">
<article>
	<title>Building from source</title>
	<para>
		To build from source, first obtain the source code from either:
	</para>
	<itemizedlist>
		<listitem><para><ulink url="http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=111957">Source distribution download</ulink></para></listitem>
		<listitem><para><ulink url="source-repository.html">Version control</ulink></para></listitem>
	</itemizedlist>
	<section>
		<title>Requirements</title>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem><para><ulink url="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html">JDK 1.6+</ulink></para></listitem>
			<listitem><para><ulink url="http://maven.apache.org/download.html">Maven 3.0+</ulink></para></listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
	</section>
	<section>
		<title>Building the JAR</title>
		<programlisting>mvn package</programlisting>
		<para>
			 The generated jar file resides in the <filename>target</filename> directory.
		</para>
	</section>
	<section>
		<title>Building the project site/documentation</title>
		<programlisting>mvn site</programlisting>
		<para>
			The generated documentation resides in the <filename>target/site</filename> directory.
		</para>
	</section>
</article>